node.text: in nature, no makeup, comfy clothes- this is my happy place. Every time I feel overwhelmed, sad, or anxious I make it a priority to get myself outside and I always feel healed. Nature is what kept me sane in 2019. I know this picture isn’t *sexy* or particularly striking but this is the real me. I’m going to try to post more about the real me (which sometimes is me in a bikini on a beach & sometimes is not) in 2020.. if you’re not interested feel free to unfollow. Otherwise- I’d love to hear what kept you going in 2019?? #nature #hike #beach #walking #yoga
